org.androidtransfuse.processor
Class ScopedTransactionWorker<V,R>

java.lang.Object
  org.androidtransfuse.processor.ScopedTransactionWorker<V,R>
All Implemented Interfaces:
TransactionWorker<V,R>
public class ScopedTransactionWorker<V,R>
extends Object
implements TransactionWorker<V,R>

Executes the given instance of a TransactionWorker with in a code generation scoped transaction. A unique instance of CodeModel is supplied in this scope which is used to generate code at the end of the transaction. If a TransactionRuntimeException is thrown this transaction will effectively reset and allow the TransactionWorker to be retried at a later code generation round.

Author:
John Ericksen
